app-level conditional call groups to an ancestor's location -- GROUPDUMP hostrun 156
evidence, see module docstring) -- FILE and NAME are what both engines prove correctly,
so Tier 2 file+name density agreement is the secondary agreement gauge; Tier 1 line-exact
(above) is now the headline, per refinement (3).
registry=N THIRD COLUMN is CONTEXT ONLY (distinct static call sites for that file+name)
